### ğŸ§  Project Objectives
- Understand and explore the *Fake vs. True* news dataset.  
- Perform *text preprocessing* (cleaning, tokenization, stopword removal).  
- Extract features using *TF-IDF* or *Bag of Words*.  
- Train *classification models* (Logistic Regression, Naive Bayes, etc.).  
- Evaluate model performance with accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score.

